{"tid":1261692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跑馬地城巴發現可疑物品 EOD到場調查","createTime":"2019-06-27T10:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T11:01:48.000Z","uid":213167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"86aebe332c3a3ebe560f6e2b6f19fe6417f3d459","tid":1261692,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"下午5時許，一部城巴駛至跑馬地大坑道近司徒拔道時，有乘客發現車廂內有一箱可疑物品，通知車長報案。警方接報後，派出爆炸品處理課（EOD）專家到場調查。<br />\n受事件影響，大坑道來回方向介乎藍塘道與司徒拔道迴旋處之間的全線現已封閉。 受影響巴士路線須改道行駛。運輸署呼籲駕駛人士考慮改用其他道路。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190627/large/1561631406_8616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190627%2Flarge%2F1561631406_8616.jpg&h=4d0da653&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"646921675bdc371a45ad729b8edac47e38f1bb89","tid":1261692,"uid":230890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cd63206ab10d648d123fa12413108a798df597f","tid":1261692,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a61c9516c32ddd0b54bd0862d967d9e3b685b06c","tid":1261692,"uid":1354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3cdce6b93cda260a69f43e18e5f839a3cafba8","tid":1261692,"uid":82947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"奉女警籲真係炸警總？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}